<p>INTER- is one of the strongest bingo stems in Scrabble. Because it uses 5 of the most common tiles in the bag, you'll frequently find yourself holding I-N-T-E-R naturally. Recognising this pattern on your rack is key to consistent bingo scoring.</p>

